itunes:title: Human Events Daily - Oct 6 2021 - Your Military Briefing on the Taiwan Crisis
title: Human Events Daily - Oct 6 2021 - Your Military Briefing on the Taiwan Crisis
description:
It’s time for a briefing on what exactly is going on with China and Taiwan, we have a shade war update involving John Kerry dissing President Biden being unaware of the tension between the U.S. and France after the AUKUS submarine deal, the Facebook whistleblower calls for a federal agency to oversee social media, plus we break down the various pressures faced by Chairman Xi including the recent power outages. 



Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
